163
00:09:27,024 --> 00:09:29,825
(Monkey King)
of our great artist, Mr. Chen.

164
00:09:30,144 --> 00:09:31,104
Everyone, take a look.

165
00:09:32,184 --> 00:09:33,344
Take it as a warning.

166
00:09:34,625 --> 00:09:35,545
