191
00:10:22,144 --> 00:10:22,785
Right here?

192
00:10:23,625 --> 00:10:24,545
But the background...

193
00:10:24,545 --> 00:10:25,384
It's okay.

194
00:10:26,224 --> 00:10:27,505
I won't draw anymore, okay?

195
00:10:27,625 --> 00:10:28,984
Fine, don't draw anymore.

196
00:10:30,945 --> 00:10:31,526
