Monkey King.

206
00:10:52,264 --> 00:10:53,465
Who is the Monkey King?

207
00:10:57,144 --> 00:10:57,785
Apologize.

208
00:11:00,384 --> 00:11:01,465
Why should I apologize?

209
00:11:03,024 --> 00:11:04,184
