he can understand quite well.

233
00:11:53,064 --> 00:11:53,785
He said that?

234
00:11:55,424 --> 00:11:56,984
In his own words, he said

235
00:11:57,224 --> 00:11:58,024
if this were his,

236
00:11:58,344 --> 00:11:59,705
