I'm very busy with work.

308
00:14:44,545 --> 00:14:45,304
I don't have time

309
00:14:45,304 --> 00:14:46,984
for the grudges between you three men.

310
00:14:47,705 --> 00:14:48,224
Fine,

311
00:14:48,705 --> 00:14:50,344
